For those looking for a Brief, Wordstar, 
Epsilon editor for Windows, your search is 
over. Features include, MDI support, status 
and toolbar, syntax color highlighting, in 
edit compile, automatic backup, file restore 
on startup, error listing, undo/redo, search,
replace, bookmarks, column, block and stream 
marking, quick help feature, fast loading, 
support for grep and C TAGS. All this and 
much more.
